---
title: Loaded Pork Chilli & Brown Rice Bowl with Cheddar Cheese & Sour Cream
description: This fantastic bowl starts with fluffy brown rice and adds a soul-satisfying chilli made with pork mince, warming spices and veggies to make it whole. With the addition of Cheddar cheese and a cucumber salsa, we can guarantee deliciousness in every bite.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/loaded-pork-black-bean-chilli-e91accd3.jpg
